SAMPLE      Sample consists of six identical 29-mm-diameter,
            0.06 g/cm**2 thick disks, placed at 1-cm intervals
            along neutron beam axis.
ERR-ANALYS (ERR-T)     Total Error, includes:
            -statistical error,
